<h2>Good to see you</h2>

<p>
  <%- if @order.performance.production.theater.is_default? %>
    Thanks for coming by to see <i><%= @order.performance.production.name %></i>.
  <%- else %>
    Thanks for coming by to see <i><%= @order.performance.production.name %>,</i> presented by <%= @order.performance.production.theater.name %>.
  <%- end %>
  I hope you had a good evening and will return soon (there are a few suggestions in
  the sidebar on the right, but check our website for all upcoming events). Unless
  you've signed up for our email list, this is the last email you'll get from us in
  regards to order <%= @order.id %>.
  <%= raw @order.performance.production.follow_up_text unless @order.performance.production.follow_up_text.blank? %>
</p>
<%= render :partial=>'core_followup' %>
